# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee11.rpy:4
translate portuguese mrsmcgee11_ee474ea1:

    # "In English class, Mrs. McGee has us working on our essays in class again."
    "Na aula de Inglês, a Sra. McGee pede-nos para trabalharmos nas nossas redações novamente."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee11.rpy:5
translate portuguese mrsmcgee11_aaf24ec9:

    # "She walks around the room answering questions from any students and looking over their essays."
    "Ela anda pela sala a responder a perguntas dos alunos e a rever as suas redações."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee11.rpy:8
translate portuguese mrsmcgee11_5f37473f:

    # "When she gets to me, she leans in, passes me a note, and whispers."
    "Quando chega até mim, inclina-se, passa-me um bilhete e sussurra."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee11.rpy:9
translate portuguese mrsmcgee11_5ea92b9a:

    # et "I enjoyed having you over the other night."
    et "Gostei muito de te ter em casa na outra noite."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee11.rpy:10
translate portuguese mrsmcgee11_a3ce88ea:

    # et "Give me a call some time if you want to visit again."
    et "Liga-me um dia destes se quiseres visitar-me outra vez."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee11.rpy:12
translate portuguese mrsmcgee11_ca2a0e41:

    # "I take a look at the note and see that she's written her phone number down on it. I'll have to add her to my cell phone later."
    "Dou uma olhadela no bilhete e vejo que ela escreveu o número de telefone nele. Vou ter de a adicionar ao meu telemóvel mais tarde."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee11.rpy:13
translate portuguese mrsmcgee11_f9bd1236:

    # "I'd definitely like to see more of her."
    "Gostaria mesmo de a ver mais vezes."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee11.rpy:15
translate portuguese mrsmcgee11_2c651ab1:

    # "After her class, I continue on with the rest of my school day and eventually leave to go to work."
    "Depois da aula dela, continuo com o resto do meu dia letivo e, por fim, saio para ir trabalhar."

